Short about the script:

The script is not only for fun, but also as a tool for the creating of scripts. In main tab is search TextBox that searches for the function name, but in the Alpha version searches for description. Also in the script there is a bypass for anti console, anti cheet Adonis and more. But something terrible can hide behind this script

I hope that this time I did it well
